  "text": "For large-scale UA-FLP problems, a genetic algorithm combined with a decomposition strategy was proposed in [CITATION_1] . Compared with basic genetic algorithm, the experiments in the paper showed that the proposed approach had an average solution improvement of 6% or 7% for large-scale instances with 90 or 100 facilities.",
